  <name>Galliard</name>
  <summary>A GNOME client for Music Player Daemon</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Galliard is a modern GNOME client for Music Player Daemon (MPD). It provides
      a clean and intuitive interface to control your music collection with
      features like album art display, playlist management, and media key support.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Browse your music library by artists, albums, and files</li>
      <li>Queue management</li>
      <li>Album art display</li>
      <li>Media key integration</li>
      <li>System tray support</li>
      <li>GNOME desktop integration</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <developer id="net.jdieter">
    <name>Jonathan Dieter</name>
  </developer>
